nodes.text: Pune Zignat was a male Aqualish and a chief weapons technician who helped Lok Durd to test his new defoliator missiles on Maridun. During the Defense of Maridun, he relayed the firing orders to the B1-Series battle droids operating the Defoliator. He managed to survive the battle, but was captured along with Durd. He also wore a pair of electronic goggles, similar to Saak'ak communications officer Tey How's goggles.
